cessful amnesty schemes and rebates for timely taxpayers. The Cidco and Panchavati divisions led the collections.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/nashiks-property-tax-revenue-hits-record-287-crore-with-10-rise/129970795?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-85598/129970795.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}